high_descs: Turn around, walk to bath tub, turn right, walk to bath tub, turn left, walk to counter
Turn around, walk forward one step, turn around
Open drawer below sink, place cleaner inside, close drawer
anns.task_desc: Pick up cleaner from counter and place below in drawer

high_descs: Turn to the left and turn left again to walk to the sink.
Pick up the spray bottle from the sink counter.
Turn around completely and walk a bit forward. Turn back around to face the sink counter.
Open the cabinet and place the spray bottle inside.
anns.task_desc: Move the spray bottle under the sink counter.

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the toilet, then turn left and walk over to the right side of the sink counter in front of you.
Pick up the white spray bottle off of the counter.
Turn left and take a step forward, then turn left again and walk across the room, then turn right and take a step forward and turn right again to face the counter.
Open the right drawer below the counter and put the white spray bottle inside, then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Move a white spray bottle into a drawer.
